text: Cymatonycha castanea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1874. It is known from Costa Rica, Honduras, and Guatemala.BioLib.cz - Cymatonycha castanea. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1874
title: Cymatonycha castanea
